    {
      "question": "What is the ideaForge Technology IPO?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>ideaForge Technology IPO<!-- --> is a <b>main-board<!-- --> <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> of <!-- -->8441764<!-- --> equity shares</b> of the face value of ₹<!-- -->10<!-- --> aggregating up to ₹<!-- -->567.29<!-- --> Crores. The issue is priced at <span>₹672 per share</span>. The minimum order quantity is <!-- -->22<!-- -->.</p><p>The <!-- -->IPO<!-- --> <b>opens on <!-- -->June 26, 2023</b>, and <b>closes on <!-- -->June 30, 2023</b>.</p><p>Link Intime India Private Ltd<!-- --> is the registrar for the <!-- -->IPO<!-- -->. The shares are proposed to be listed on <!-- -->BSE, NSE<!-- -->.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "How to apply in ideaForge Technology IPO through Zerodha?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>Zerodha customers can apply online in <!-- -->ideaForge Technology IPO<!-- --> using UPI as a payment gateway. Zerodha customers can apply in <!-- -->ideaForge Technology IPO<!-- --> by login into Zerodha Console (back office) and submitting an IPO application form.</p><p><strong>Steps to apply in <!-- -->ideaForge Technology IPO<!-- --> through Zerodha</strong></p><ol><li>Visit the Zerodha website and login to Console.</li><li>Go to Portfolio and click the IPOs link.</li><li>Go to the '<!-- -->ideaForge Technology IPO<!-- -->' row and click the 'Bid' button.</li><li>Enter your UPI ID, Quantity, and Price.</li><li>Submit IPO application form.</li><li>Visit the UPI App (net banking or BHIM) to approve the mandate.</li></ol><p>Visit <a href=\"/broker/zerodha/ipo/18/\" title=\"Zerodha IPO Application Process Review\">Zerodha IPO Application Process Review</a> for more detail.</p></div>"
    },
    {
      "question": "When ideaForge Technology IPO will open?",
      "answer": "<div itemprop=\"text\"><p>The ideaForge Technology IPO opens on June 26, 2023 and closes on June 30, 2023.</p></div>"
